'From Squeak3.1alpha of 5 February 2001 [latest update: #3752] on 1 March 2001 at 11:20:22 am'!"Change Set:		expungePreference-swDate:			1 March 2001Author:			Scott WallaceProvides a mechanism for removing a preference."!!Preferences class methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sw 2/27/2001 20:49'!expungePreferenceNamed: aSymbol	"Remove all memory of the given preference symbol in my various structures."	| aMethod |	FlagDictionary removeKey: aSymbol ifAbsent: [].	HelpDictionary removeKey: aSymbol ifAbsent: [].	FlagsHeldByProjects removeKey: aSymbol ifAbsent: [].	(self class organization listAtCategoryNamed: 'initial values' asSymbol) do:		[:aSelector | aSelector numArgs = 0 ifTrue:			[aMethod _ self class compiledMethodAt: aSelector.			(aMethod literals includes: aSymbol)				ifTrue:					[self class removeSelector: aSelector.					Transcript cr; show: 'Removed method Preferences.', aSelector]]].	self resetCategoryInfo."Preferences expungePreferenceNamed: #tileToggleInBrowsers"! !!Preferences class methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sw 2/27/2001 20:33'!initializeHelpMessages	"Initialize the preferences help messages from the initialization information found"  	HelpDictionary _ IdentityDictionary new.	self allPreferenceInitializationSpecs do:		[:quad |			quad size >= 4 ifTrue:				[HelpDictionary at: quad first put: quad fourth]]	"Preferences initializeHelpMessages"! !